{"tid":179863,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[煮飯新手求教學]岩岩整左個牛肉飯，好撚難食","createTime":"2017-03-30T13:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T18:25:37.000Z","uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"824f1392f1974badb5482ebc907572854965ab0b","tid":179863,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"打返d step出黎先<br />\n1)將牛肉切粒，煎到半熟<br />\n2)李錦記黑椒醬開水，比例1:1<br />\n3)煲飯，用2)開既黑椒醬，同時落埋半熟牛肉<br />\n<br />\n整完之後有以下問題<br />\n1)牛肉太熟，好硬<br />\n2)飯太乾，又係好硬<br />\n3)有飯焦<br />\n4)黑椒味唔明顯<br />\n<br />\n下次點整先解決到呢4個問題？"},{"pid":"56540244fe1cff66b551b3102334ad6a169598e0","tid":179863,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打返d step出黎先<br />\n1)將牛肉切粒，煎到半熟<br />\n2)李錦記黑椒醬開水，比例1:1<br />\n3)煲飯，用2)開既黑椒醬，同時落埋半熟牛肉一齊煲<br />\n<br />\n整完之後有以下問題<br />\n1)牛肉太熟，好硬<br />\n2)飯太乾，又係好硬<br />\n3)有飯焦<br />\n4)黑椒味唔明顯<br />\n<br />\n下次點整先解決到呢4個問題？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5efe160bf1dc15fe7a8e0786ecb7440f2be682f4","tid":179863,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"落街食"},{"pid":"3344e810145f5d18856816a90b57f97fb4d51ca8","tid":179863,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:12:11.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2445ae4c9acf87bea91014cb021911f3ba1965fc","tid":179863,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n網名黎嫁je<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4313851c0b1c3e67c194d45c7ca20ace8f2cf0","tid":179863,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"牛肉唔好煎到咁熟<br />\n加多d水<br />\n換個靚d既電飯煲<br />\n加多d黑椒"},{"pid":"0f21fa71aa39c909cb6e814e5461c996b46e336b","tid":179863,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打返d step出黎先<br />\n1)將牛肉切粒，煎到半熟<br />\n2)李錦記黑椒醬開水，比例1:1<br />\n3)煲飯，用2)開既黑椒醬，同時落埋半熟牛肉<br />\n<br />\n整完之後有以下問題<br />\n1)牛肉太熟，好硬<br />\n2)飯太乾，又係好硬<br />\n3)有飯焦<br />\n4)黑椒味唔明顯<br />\n<br />\n下次點整先解決到呢4個問題？</blockquote><br />\n1）落多D鬆肉粉<br />\n2）落多D水<br />\n3）換過個電飯煲<br />\n4）落多D黑椒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2332b96ff78d00c1566d9a044c33f5532342e5cc","tid":179863,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛肉唔好煎到咁熟<br />\n加多d水<br />\n換個靚d既電飯煲<br />\n加多d黑椒</blockquote><br />\n睇得出Ching都係煮開餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd787c61bf881e41d82ee33774ff68ad7cb5341","tid":179863,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打返d step出黎先<br />\n1)將牛肉切粒，煎到半熟<br />\n2)李錦記黑椒醬開水，比例1:1<br />\n3)煲飯，用2)開既黑椒醬，同時落埋半熟牛肉<br />\n<br />\n整完之後有以下問題<br />\n1)牛肉太熟，好硬<br />\n2)飯太乾，又係好硬<br />\n3)有飯焦<br />\n4)黑椒味唔明顯<br />\n<br />\n下次點整先解決到呢4個問題？</blockquote><br />\n1）落多D鬆肉粉<br />\n2）落多D水<br />\n3）換過個電飯煲<br />\n4）落多D黑椒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ef548250a63dafe25c640e92fdcab4862b3934","tid":179863,"uid":12556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"牛肉煎到3成夠  , 5成再落鑊住既話 好易overcook 新手未必掌握到<br />\n<br />\n飯硬係你唔夠水既問題  我自己靠手感 無計過落幾多<br />\n去問下你阿媽平時落幾多水煲飯<br />\n<br />\n要黑椒味重 , 大火黑椒牛油起鑊 聞到黑椒味就轉細火落你個枝汁 之後先加水 ,加半份水先 你覺得咸先再加<br />\n最後落少少糖釣味 <br />\n我自己係落蠔油雞粉糖老抽<br />\n<br />\n 最後記者會較好哂味先落牛肉  , 落完兜勻就埋茨收隊<br />\n過程唔好過30秒<br />\n唔係你啲牛肉會連狗都唔食<br />\n<br />\n垃圾廚房佬留名"},{"pid":"b27ce779795b5832ddc21aea3abf4622a2e0fb9e","tid":179863,"uid":12556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n最後記<span style=\"color: blue;\">得</span>會較好哂味先落牛肉  , 落完兜勻就埋茨收隊<br />\n過程唔好過30秒<br />\n唔係你啲牛肉會連狗都唔食<br />\n<br />\n垃圾廚房佬留名</blockquote><br />\nOn9打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1c9059a5e532a92f20263990d26a536d9d1bd5","tid":179863,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛肉煎到3成夠  , 5成再落鑊住既話 好易overcook 新手未必掌握到<br />\n<br />\n飯硬係你唔夠水既問題  我自己靠手感 無計過落幾多<br />\n去問下你阿媽平時落幾多水煲飯<br />\n<br />\n要黑椒味重 , 大火黑椒牛油起鑊 聞到黑椒味就轉細火落你個枝汁 之後先加水 ,加半份水先 你覺得咸先再加<br />\n最後落少少糖釣味 <br />\n我自己係落蠔油雞粉糖老抽<br />\n<br />\n 最後記者會較好哂味先落牛肉  , 落完兜勻就埋茨收隊<br />\n過程唔好過30秒<br />\n唔係你啲牛肉會連狗都唔食<br />\n<br />\n垃圾廚房佬留名</blockquote><br />\n長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa9a6e83eee6b059352e7aff9966ae0112db183","tid":179863,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3a83017f81d102eb10f2833572830615d99826","tid":179863,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛肉煎到3成夠  , 5成再落鑊住既話 好易overcook 新手未必掌握到<br />\n<br />\n飯硬係你唔夠水既問題  我自己靠手感 無計過落幾多<br />\n去問下你阿媽平時落幾多水煲飯<br />\n<br />\n要黑椒味重 , 大火黑椒牛油起鑊 聞到黑椒味就轉細火落你個枝汁 之後先加水 ,加半份水先 你覺得咸先再加<br />\n最後落少少糖釣味 <br />\n我自己係落蠔油雞粉糖老抽<br />\n<br />\n 最後記者會較好哂味先落牛肉  , 落完兜勻就埋茨收隊<br />\n過程唔好過30秒<br />\n唔係你啲牛肉會連狗都唔食<br />\n<br />\n垃圾廚房佬留名</blockquote><br />\n學到野"},{"pid":"96e975d2b4afea6c03e5e52d8b9ecff48c2631bc","tid":179863,"uid":15719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"朱紅的水滴姐姐提提你"},{"pid":"675698273f642a578ad02fc6792ee205ed9074d2","tid":179863,"uid":12556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:51:06.000Z","msg":"同埋唔建議牛肉連飯一齊煲<br />\n你依味始終唔係蒸餸 , 蒸完出黎會無左落鑊炒個種香味<br />\n寧願蒸完牛 再淋落飯上面 類似蓋飯咁樣會較好"},{"pid":"84c29d854f129850962515436b15ac0c611e81b6","tid":179863,"uid":12556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n寧願<span style=\"color: blue;\">煮</span>完牛 </blockquote>"},{"pid":"b0f2feca55dc5ce8e6ce3a448b0b53f491ae7e03","tid":179863,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26f443dadb868c6d78ddb1e6bfdd425abeb56c31","tid":179863,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"我娘親煮法：<br />\n<br />\n牛肉切粒，醃一會兒，之後大火落鑊煎至一邊金黃，約五成熟，拎起<br />\n<br />\n同一個鑊，炒洋蔥絲，少少乾蔥，軟身後加黑椒汁爆香，加少少水，汁滾落牛兜一下<br />\n<br />\n上碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fb2b2acdcc6e73541a1a0c931ac845cfed843d","tid":179863,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:25:37.000Z","msg":"用肥牛方便又平又唔怕好老"}]}